    "notes": "This series contains two distinct products that should be split:\n\n1. **Löwenzahn CLASSICS (14 albums)**: Re-releases of the original Hörspiele featuring Peter Lustig, released 2023. These have different titles (e.g., 'Peter und der Tanz der Vampire' vs 'Abenteuer Feuerland'), longer track counts (16-17 tracks vs 13 tracks), and are clearly branded as CLASSICS.\n\n2. **New Löwenzahn episodes (17 albums)**: Modern episodes featuring Fritz Fuchs as the protagonist, released 2021-2026. These are numbered Episode 01-17 and have different story content.\n\nThe two versions share episode numbers but have completely different content - they are NOT duplicates. A parent looking for the classic Peter Lustig episodes would be confused to find Fritz Fuchs episodes mixed in, and vice versa.\n\nEpisodes 15-17 in the main series feature Fritz Fuchs (not Peter Lustig), confirming this is the modern continuation of the series.",
